"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/627321","Department for Education","false","2016-11-08","<p>This is a matter for Ofsted. I have asked Her Majesty’s Chief Inspector, Sir Michael Wilshaw, to write to the The Hon Member for South Shields (Emma Lewell-Buck MP) with the information requested. A copy of his reply will be placed in the House library.</p>","Crewe and Nantwich","Edward Timpson","51598","2016-11-08T17:50:43.63Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/627321/answer","Biography information for Edward Timpson","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/627321/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/627321/answer",,,,,,,,"60","Education","Education","2016-11-02","Foster Care","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Education, how many foster carers there are in the UK by (a) region or constituent nation, (b) local authority area and (c) type and level of foster carers.","false","Biography information for Mrs Emma Lewell-Buck","South Shields","Mrs Emma Lewell-Buck","51599"
